					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Zepper wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I didn't know about wrapping to zero if the sprite address is incremented from $FF. Is this documented??</div><br />Well, sprite DMA is just a stream of writes to $2004, so if address didn't wrap it wouldn't work at all if one didn't set $2003 before each write to $4014. Also, it would require more logic to do something different than wrapping for a 8-bit up counter.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

